com.technototes.control.gamepad

Class AbstractGamepad<T extends GamepadButton,U extends GamepadAxis>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.technototes.control.gamepad.AbstractGamepad<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The class for the button components on the gamepad
    U - The class for the axis components on the gamepad
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Periodic
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleGamepad

    public abstract class AbstractGamepad<T extends GamepadButton,U extends GamepadAxis>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Periodic
    A class to extend gamepads from, it does the internal processing for you.
